WEBVTT

00:52.640 --> 00:54.280
You still haven't reached her?

00:54.280 --> 00:54.880
Yeah.

00:55.000 --> 00:56.560
Her phone is unreachable.

00:58.800 --> 00:59.480
It's fine.

00:59.560 --> 01:01.290
She must be with her classmates

01:01.320 --> 01:02.400
and didn't check her phone.

01:02.400 --> 01:03.680
What classmates?

01:03.800 --> 01:04.400
I'm telling you.

01:04.400 --> 01:07.240
I've noticed something off about her these past two days.

01:07.240 --> 01:08.120
Finals.

01:08.120 --> 01:09.280
Finals crunch.

01:09.280 --> 01:11.240
Her state is naturally different from usual.

01:11.240 --> 01:12.800
Can't she study at home?

01:12.880 --> 01:14.320
I held back and didn't scold her.

01:14.320 --> 01:15.850
At least put my mind at ease.

01:18.800 --> 01:19.760
Why did you come out?

01:19.760 --> 01:20.680
Have you finished your homework?

01:20.680 --> 01:22.480
I'm going to the kitchen to find something to eat.

01:22.480 --> 01:24.000
It's late. Don't eat.

01:24.160 --> 01:25.280
I'm hungry.

01:26.560 --> 01:27.620
Don't eat too much.

01:29.760 --> 01:30.320
Mom.

01:30.800 --> 01:32.360
My classmate's dad...

01:32.520 --> 01:34.360
taught us how to play the ocarina.

01:34.360 --> 01:36.400
I can play 'Twinkle, Twinkle, Little Star' now.

01:36.400 --> 01:37.680
Aunt, Mom,

01:37.759 --> 01:39.690
do you want me to play it for you two?

01:39.880 --> 01:40.560
Xing,

01:40.560 --> 01:41.759
it's already very late.

01:41.759 --> 01:43.960
Let's not disturb the neighbors, okay?

01:44.120 --> 01:46.120
Waiting for my sister together again?

01:46.120 --> 01:46.720
By the way,

01:47.520 --> 01:48.800
is it safe around here?

01:48.880 --> 01:50.280
How about I go meet her at the intersection?

01:50.280 --> 01:51.640
What if it's not safe coming back?

01:51.640 --> 01:52.759
The security is very good here.

01:52.759 --> 01:53.320
You can rest assured.

01:53.320 --> 01:54.080
It's fine.

01:54.200 --> 01:56.720
Someone drops my sister off every time she comes back.

01:56.720 --> 01:57.280
What?

01:58.200 --> 02:00.930
Nothing. I'll go back to my room to eat my sausage.

02:08.560 --> 02:09.440
Mr. Yue.

02:10.320 --> 02:12.050
This is Zhao Xiaocen's mother.

02:12.720 --> 02:14.320
She said she's at Weijiayao these two days.

02:14.320 --> 02:15.440
Did you know that?

02:16.079 --> 02:16.840
Yes, I know.

02:18.079 --> 02:18.940
It's like this.

02:19.560 --> 02:20.800
She hasn't come home yet.

02:20.800 --> 02:22.000
And I can't reach her on the phone either.

02:22.000 --> 02:23.329
So I'm getting worried.

02:23.400 --> 02:23.760
I was thinking,

02:23.760 --> 02:25.960
should I go to Weijiayao to look for her?

02:28.240 --> 02:29.400
Mr. Liang?

02:30.320 --> 02:31.400
Okay.

02:31.560 --> 02:32.560
I have the number.

02:32.840 --> 02:33.440
Okay.

02:33.720 --> 02:34.560
Goodbye.

02:35.600 --> 02:36.560
Mr. Liang.

02:36.560 --> 02:37.320
Sister,

02:37.520 --> 02:38.520
stop calling.

02:38.560 --> 02:40.640
You're making it so awkward for Xiaocen.

02:40.640 --> 02:42.160
If something happens,

02:42.160 --> 02:44.560
it won't be a matter of being awkward or not.

02:44.760 --> 02:46.720
Look, it's not even 10 o'clock yet.

02:46.840 --> 02:48.640
Can we just wait a little longer?

02:52.120 --> 02:53.560
Let me ask her classmate.

02:57.840 --> 02:59.040
Wu Jing,

02:59.200 --> 03:01.440
is our Xiaocen with you?

03:05.560 --> 03:08.080
I wonder how things are on the mountain.

03:08.880 --> 03:09.610
Don't worry.

03:10.560 --> 03:11.560
You also saw Guan Lin

03:11.560 --> 03:14.290
fire the 'Three Rams' piece by himself last time.

03:15.000 --> 03:17.060
But that wasn't Weijiayao after all.

03:17.680 --> 03:18.320
Xu Xiao.

03:19.720 --> 03:20.560
What if,

03:21.360 --> 03:22.560
just what if,

03:24.079 --> 03:25.740
he doesn't succeed this time.

03:26.280 --> 03:27.680
What would the impact be?

03:31.720 --> 03:33.850
Word will spread quickly in the market

03:34.280 --> 03:36.280
that Guan Lin can't hold Weijiayao.

03:38.440 --> 03:40.640
Then the pressure will be even greater.

03:43.880 --> 03:45.880
When Master Wei made this decision,

03:46.440 --> 03:48.240
he must have thought of this too.

03:48.880 --> 03:49.800
But he also knew

03:50.520 --> 03:52.180
he didn't have much time left.

03:52.920 --> 03:54.180
He had to take a chance.

03:55.440 --> 03:58.720
Now we just hope the Kiln God blesses us.

04:13.440 --> 04:14.370
Xiaocen is back.

04:16.480 --> 04:17.740
Xiaocen, you're back.

04:19.880 --> 04:21.079
Sis, Xiaocen is back.

04:27.680 --> 04:28.920
I'm sorry.

04:31.120 --> 04:32.920
My phone died during the day,

04:33.760 --> 04:35.120
and it shut down.

04:39.080 --> 04:39.640
Xiaocen,

04:40.360 --> 04:41.220
have you eaten?

04:42.040 --> 04:42.920
It's hot, isn't it?

04:42.920 --> 04:44.980
Summer in Jingdezhen is the hottest.

04:45.080 --> 04:47.000
I made some iced mung bean soup for you.

04:47.000 --> 04:47.680
I'll go get it for you.

04:47.680 --> 04:48.940
Don't let her drink it.

04:52.760 --> 04:53.520
Qingying.

04:54.320 --> 04:55.480
Go back to your room first.

04:55.480 --> 04:56.610
I need to talk to her.

04:56.680 --> 04:58.720
It's fine. I'll just stay here. Go ahead.

04:58.720 --> 05:00.180
Go back to your room first.

05:01.960 --> 05:03.040
Okay, okay.

05:25.240 --> 05:27.770
How was I supposed to know your phone was dead?

05:28.480 --> 05:29.680
I couldn't reach you.

05:29.880 --> 05:31.160
If something happened to you,

05:31.160 --> 05:33.200
do you know how worried I would be?

05:36.800 --> 05:38.120
Mom, I'm sorry.

05:40.400 --> 05:41.960
I will never do this again.

05:41.960 --> 05:42.690
Never again?

05:43.280 --> 05:45.480
How many times have you come home late recently?

05:45.480 --> 05:46.520
How many times recently

05:46.520 --> 05:48.250
have I not known where you were?

05:49.440 --> 05:50.240
Zhao Xiaocen.

05:51.520 --> 05:53.120
Before this semester ends,

05:53.480 --> 05:54.880
other than going to class,

05:54.880 --> 05:56.480
no matter where you go,

05:56.800 --> 05:58.159
you must tell me first.

05:58.360 --> 06:00.560
Otherwise, you're not going anywhere.

06:02.080 --> 06:02.760
Got it?

06:04.280 --> 06:05.240
I got it.

06:09.440 --> 06:10.360
The wind has died down.

06:10.360 --> 06:11.720
The temperature inside has dropped too.

06:11.720 --> 06:12.650
Go back and rest.

06:13.200 --> 06:14.130
Go back, go back.

06:14.200 --> 06:14.600
Okay.

06:15.320 --> 06:15.800
Go back.

06:17.600 --> 06:18.330
Master Guan.

06:18.600 --> 06:20.730
It's your turn to sit in this chair now.

06:23.560 --> 06:24.080
Go back.

06:24.320 --> 06:25.250
Go get some rest.

06:31.600 --> 06:33.680
Wet wood and dry wood

06:33.760 --> 06:35.800
must never be burned together.

06:35.960 --> 06:37.480
Only if you fire it correctly

06:37.480 --> 06:38.480
can the porcelain

06:38.880 --> 06:41.720
be as green as jade, as clear as a mirror,

06:42.000 --> 06:44.200
as thin as paper, and sound like a chime.

06:44.880 --> 06:46.040
As for porcelain,

06:46.040 --> 06:47.480
its unique charm

06:47.720 --> 06:50.480
lies in clay, kiln, fire, and wood

06:50.560 --> 06:52.490
and their delicate relationship.

06:52.640 --> 06:53.800
And the kiln master

06:54.800 --> 06:57.760
is the one who adjusts this balance.

07:17.040 --> 07:17.900
That's enough.

07:19.280 --> 07:20.560
Stop adding firewood.

07:21.160 --> 07:21.820
Put it down.

07:23.800 --> 07:24.640
I tell you,

07:25.360 --> 07:26.690
after sealing the door,

07:27.120 --> 07:29.720
you shouldn't add too much firewood.

07:30.480 --> 07:32.810
At this point, you have to rely on your eyes

07:32.880 --> 07:34.080
and your ears.

07:34.880 --> 07:36.200
Controlling the heat

07:36.680 --> 07:39.400
must be like cooking porridge over a slow fire.

07:40.600 --> 07:43.930
Slow fire and fine work allow the glaze to penetrate deeply.

07:45.000 --> 07:46.440
Never rush.

07:46.880 --> 07:49.000
You need to be patient.

07:49.159 --> 07:51.280
The temperature shouldn't rise too fast.

07:51.280 --> 07:52.240
Got it?

08:47.880 --> 08:48.410
Let's go.

09:08.240 --> 09:09.040
Rest assured.

09:10.080 --> 09:11.000
As for Mr. Wei,

09:11.000 --> 09:14.060
I've hired a professional caregiver to look after him.

09:14.640 --> 09:15.970
But what about you guys?

09:16.160 --> 09:17.960
It's already the end of the term.

09:18.200 --> 09:20.720
You have to review and take exams for every course.

09:20.720 --> 09:22.200
So you should focus

09:22.360 --> 09:23.820
your minds back on school.

09:24.760 --> 09:25.240
Okay.

09:26.880 --> 09:28.200
Mr. Wei hasn't woken up yet.

09:28.200 --> 09:29.200
But the doctor said there's no rush,

09:29.200 --> 09:30.530
and he's stable for now.

09:30.720 --> 09:32.450
Let's come see him another day.

09:33.760 --> 09:35.360
How are things at Weijiayao?

09:36.240 --> 09:37.600
Brother Guan Lin is keeping watch.

09:37.600 --> 09:39.330
I hope the kiln opens smoothly.

09:39.920 --> 09:40.520
I also hope

09:41.600 --> 09:42.800
Mr. Wei wakes up soon.

09:53.400 --> 09:54.660
Like stacking blocks.

09:55.760 --> 09:58.290
Stack them into the shape of the kiln opening.

10:04.640 --> 10:05.300
Add them in.

10:05.400 --> 10:05.760
Okay.

10:08.880 --> 10:09.410
Xiaocen.

10:10.000 --> 10:10.800
Manual labor is too tough.

10:10.800 --> 10:11.600
You don't need to do it.

10:11.600 --> 10:12.200
It's fine.

10:12.640 --> 10:13.840
I want to help too.

10:14.320 --> 10:15.250
Then be careful.

10:44.200 --> 10:44.640
Let me.

10:49.200 --> 10:50.720
Guan Lin is much steadier now.

10:50.720 --> 10:53.250
He's getting more and more of Mr. Wei's style.

10:56.440 --> 10:57.040
Masters.

10:57.800 --> 10:58.920
Xiaocen, Xu Xiao,

10:59.360 --> 11:00.090
let's go eat.

11:00.840 --> 11:01.120
Go ahead.

11:01.120 --> 11:01.840
Okay.

11:03.640 --> 11:04.280
Good work.

11:04.760 --> 11:05.320
Good work.

11:05.320 --> 11:05.960
Go ahead.

11:05.960 --> 11:07.020
Let's go, Xiaocen.

11:07.600 --> 11:08.040
Go on.

11:17.080 --> 11:17.880
Xu Xiao.

11:21.080 --> 11:22.040
Xu Xiao.

11:28.080 --> 11:28.680
Xiaocen.

11:30.640 --> 11:31.170
Xiaocen.

11:31.480 --> 11:32.010
Xiaocen.

11:32.640 --> 11:33.170
Xiaocen.

11:34.200 --> 11:35.200
Xiaocen, wake up.

11:51.120 --> 11:51.560
Ma'am.

12:00.600 --> 12:01.240
Cencen.

12:04.920 --> 12:06.580
Cencen, what happened to you?

12:07.000 --> 12:08.130
Ma'am, don't worry.

12:09.160 --> 12:11.280
She just fell asleep after taking her medicine.

12:11.280 --> 12:13.540
The doctor said it's chronic urticaria.

12:53.840 --> 12:54.320
Ma'am.

12:55.640 --> 12:56.640
My name is Xu Xiao.

12:57.320 --> 12:58.780
I'm Xiaocen's classmate.

13:00.640 --> 13:01.760
I just went through her phone

13:01.760 --> 13:03.020
and found your number.

13:07.280 --> 13:08.280
Ma'am, I'm sorry.

13:08.800 --> 13:09.660
I was careless.

13:10.200 --> 13:10.840
I noticed earlier

13:10.840 --> 13:12.040
that Xiaocen had red bumps on her body.

13:12.040 --> 13:13.200
I thought it was just from the summer heat and humidity.

13:13.200 --> 13:13.960
Do you think

13:16.040 --> 13:17.160
you're a doctor?

13:17.840 --> 13:19.120
Do you know what hives are,

13:19.120 --> 13:20.400
and what causes them?

13:21.320 --> 13:22.120
Lack of sleep,

13:22.640 --> 13:24.040
extreme fatigue, and mental stress

13:24.040 --> 13:25.520
will all worsen her allergies.

13:25.520 --> 13:27.080
There are also external factors.

13:27.080 --> 13:28.920
Weather, food, dust,

13:29.360 --> 13:30.040
and UV rays

13:30.400 --> 13:31.730
will make it even worse.

13:33.040 --> 13:34.370
The red spots on her body

13:35.080 --> 13:36.560
are caused by vasodilation,

13:36.560 --> 13:37.960
and can also cause edema.

13:38.160 --> 13:40.320
Luckily, it was only on her skin this time.

13:40.320 --> 13:41.560
If it had occurred in her throat,

13:41.560 --> 13:43.520
you know it could have suffocated her.

13:43.520 --> 13:44.580
Do you understand?

13:48.960 --> 13:49.560
I'm sorry.

13:50.960 --> 13:51.960
It's all my fault.

13:54.560 --> 13:54.960
Okay.

13:57.040 --> 13:58.440
Let me ask you something.

13:58.680 --> 13:59.680
Are you currently

14:00.400 --> 14:02.330
getting very close to our Xiaocen?

14:09.120 --> 14:09.580
Auntie,

14:10.720 --> 14:11.580
I like Xiaocen.

14:12.520 --> 14:13.320
I am serious about her.

14:13.320 --> 14:14.400
Do you know that saying this

14:14.400 --> 14:15.440
means you have to take responsibility?

14:15.440 --> 14:15.960
I know.

14:16.120 --> 14:17.050
What do you know?

14:18.400 --> 14:19.400
Do you really understand Xiaocen?

14:19.400 --> 14:21.000
Do you know about our family?

14:21.160 --> 14:22.690
How long have you known her?

14:23.600 --> 14:24.960
Now you have her leaving early and coming home late,

14:24.960 --> 14:26.280
not even resting on weekends.

14:26.280 --> 14:28.200
Last time, she was bedridden with stomach pain.

14:28.200 --> 14:30.260
And now, she ended up in the hospital.

14:31.920 --> 14:33.920
Is this how you show you're serious?

14:36.920 --> 14:37.980
Auntie, I'm sorry.

14:38.840 --> 14:39.440
I promise

14:39.440 --> 14:40.760
this will never happen again.

14:40.760 --> 14:43.220
I will definitely take good care of Xiaocen.

14:43.360 --> 14:44.420
Where are you from?

14:46.200 --> 14:46.930
Jingdezhen.

14:48.320 --> 14:49.720
What about your parents?

14:51.440 --> 14:51.970
Here too.

14:54.280 --> 14:55.160
So,

14:56.160 --> 14:57.960
you were born in Jingdezhen,

14:58.640 --> 14:59.760
went to college here,

14:59.760 --> 15:00.760
and in the future,

15:01.000 --> 15:03.400
you won't leave Jingdezhen. Is that right?

15:17.800 --> 15:19.930
Then how will you take care of Xiaocen?

15:20.480 --> 15:21.410
Walking her home

15:21.880 --> 15:23.680
is considered taking care of her?

15:23.680 --> 15:24.480
After Xiaocen

15:25.040 --> 15:26.300
finishes her studies,

15:26.360 --> 15:28.020
I will take her away from here.

15:29.800 --> 15:32.400
I will absolutely not leave her in Jingdezhen.

16:11.280 --> 16:11.760
Guan,

16:11.920 --> 16:12.760
hurry up and eat.

16:12.760 --> 16:14.320
First, filling. Second, firing. Third, cooling.

16:14.320 --> 16:15.080
Master said

16:15.160 --> 16:16.880
the three most important things in kiln firing

16:16.880 --> 16:18.480
are filling the kiln, controlling the heat,

16:18.480 --> 16:20.160
and the proper time to cool down.

16:20.160 --> 16:21.840
It looks like the kiln needs to be cooled down soon.

16:21.840 --> 16:22.600
But you still have to eat.

16:22.600 --> 16:23.600
You guys go ahead.

16:36.080 --> 16:36.840
Xiaocen,

16:40.040 --> 16:40.840
you're awake.

16:41.680 --> 16:43.210
Are you feeling any better?

16:44.200 --> 16:44.880
Mom,

16:46.040 --> 16:47.080
why are you here?

16:47.960 --> 16:48.880
Why am I here?

16:49.120 --> 16:50.920
Look at all the rashes on your hands.

16:50.920 --> 16:52.250
You didn't even tell me.

16:53.800 --> 16:55.240
Don't move. Lie down.

16:56.280 --> 16:57.080
Get some rest.

16:59.600 --> 17:00.760
Xu Xiao,

17:05.960 --> 17:07.720
who told you to come?

17:09.640 --> 17:12.000
Uh, the hospital called me.

17:12.920 --> 17:15.119
Let me see what kind of medicine this is.

17:21.640 --> 17:22.319
You're back.

17:22.319 --> 17:22.960
Xiaocen,

17:23.480 --> 17:24.079
how are you doing?

17:24.079 --> 17:24.480
Aunt,

17:24.480 --> 17:25.200
what did the doctor say?

17:25.200 --> 17:26.280
I'm fine, Aunt.

17:26.640 --> 17:28.500
Look, my rash went away on its own.

17:28.600 --> 17:30.000
The doctor said I'm fine.

17:30.240 --> 17:31.080
Look at you.

17:31.200 --> 17:32.800
How could you be so careless?

17:33.000 --> 17:35.260
You must be careful from now on, you know?

17:42.560 --> 17:43.200
Master.

17:45.480 --> 17:47.080
The fire at Weijiayao is out.

17:48.200 --> 17:49.840
Don't you want to see if I won

17:50.080 --> 17:51.210
or lost this battle?

17:53.480 --> 17:54.920
If the firing went bad,

17:56.160 --> 17:57.520
get up and scold me.

18:08.000 --> 18:08.640
Master!

18:10.760 --> 18:11.240
Doctor!

18:12.080 --> 18:12.720
Doctor!

18:13.560 --> 18:14.240
Doctor!

18:19.480 --> 18:20.200
Cencen.

18:20.920 --> 18:21.250
Here,

18:23.880 --> 18:25.760
take the medicine the doctor prescribed.

18:25.760 --> 18:26.280
Okay.

18:26.400 --> 18:26.840
Here.

18:28.480 --> 18:29.810
Slow down, don't choke.

18:33.800 --> 18:34.400
How is it?

18:35.120 --> 18:36.050
Feeling better?

18:36.800 --> 18:37.880
Much better.

18:40.760 --> 18:41.490
That's good.

18:43.320 --> 18:45.240
I want to go back to school in a couple of days.

18:45.240 --> 18:46.770
Because I still have exams.

18:51.400 --> 18:51.920
Mom,

18:54.400 --> 18:55.040
I

18:55.760 --> 18:56.320
promise

18:56.560 --> 18:58.320
this won't happen again.

18:59.040 --> 19:00.840
I'll take good care of my body.

19:03.480 --> 19:04.120
Cencen,

19:06.040 --> 19:08.040
Mom wants to apologize to you first.

19:08.920 --> 19:11.080
Having you choose this major back then,

19:11.080 --> 19:11.520
firstly,

19:11.520 --> 19:14.040
was considering your Aunt is right in Jingdezhen.

19:14.040 --> 19:14.720
Secondly,

19:14.760 --> 19:16.090
it's because for a girl,

19:16.240 --> 19:17.480
if you choose this major,

19:17.480 --> 19:19.240
you can work in a museum in the future.

19:19.240 --> 19:20.640
It's a state-owned unit,

19:20.680 --> 19:22.610
and a clerical job is quite stable.

19:23.280 --> 19:24.280
But to be honest,

19:24.800 --> 19:26.680
I really didn't expect this major

19:26.840 --> 19:28.770
would drain so much of your energy.

19:30.200 --> 19:32.960
It was poorly considered on my part.

19:38.640 --> 19:39.160
Mom,

19:41.560 --> 19:43.020
what are you trying to say?

19:45.480 --> 19:47.010
I've already asked around.

19:47.200 --> 19:48.560
After your freshman year,

19:48.560 --> 19:50.400
you can switch majors.

19:51.000 --> 19:52.720
I want to discuss it with the school

19:52.720 --> 19:54.920
and have you transferred to museology.

19:56.800 --> 19:57.880
Mom, look,

19:59.240 --> 20:01.300
I've already studied for a semester,

20:01.920 --> 20:03.800
and I have so many friends.

20:06.640 --> 20:08.280
I don't want to switch majors.

20:08.280 --> 20:10.200
You have four years of college.

20:11.120 --> 20:12.520
You'll have plenty of chances

20:12.520 --> 20:14.050
to make new friends, right?

20:15.200 --> 20:15.960
Then I think

20:15.960 --> 20:17.760
you should discuss this with me.

20:17.880 --> 20:19.880
Aren't I discussing it with you now?

20:21.520 --> 20:22.920
This isn't a discussion.

20:23.680 --> 20:25.140
You're just informing me.

20:27.920 --> 20:28.520
You kid,

20:28.520 --> 20:30.250
how can you talk to me like this?

20:31.560 --> 20:33.000
Do you know how serious

20:33.000 --> 20:34.200
your hives were this time?

20:34.200 --> 20:35.480
If something went wrong,

20:35.480 --> 20:37.140
who would you be letting down?

20:37.160 --> 20:38.920
This time was just an accident.

20:39.840 --> 20:40.520
It seems

20:40.880 --> 20:42.800
it has nothing to do with my major, right?

20:42.800 --> 20:44.160
How does it have nothing to do with it?

20:44.160 --> 20:46.220
If you hadn't gone to that Weijiayao,

20:46.240 --> 20:47.920
if you weren't overly exhausted,

20:47.920 --> 20:49.580
this wouldn't have happened.

20:49.640 --> 20:50.320
I'm telling you,

20:50.320 --> 20:51.960
you're irresponsible with your own body,

20:51.960 --> 20:53.820
so I have to be responsible for it.

20:54.600 --> 20:55.400
Mom,

20:55.960 --> 20:58.720
I really like this major.

20:59.360 --> 21:00.560
I promise you,

21:00.840 --> 21:02.640
this won't happen again.

21:03.000 --> 21:04.400
Your dad and I have already discussed it.

21:04.400 --> 21:06.240
We've decided to change your major.

21:06.240 --> 21:08.360
Then what did you say you were discussing with me?

21:08.360 --> 21:09.290
I am your mother.

21:09.680 --> 21:11.680
You have to listen to whatever I say.

21:16.920 --> 21:17.480
Yes.

21:18.640 --> 21:19.920
I must listen to you.

21:22.080 --> 21:24.720
I've had to listen to you since I was a child.

21:28.920 --> 21:29.720
What's wrong?

21:29.960 --> 21:31.000
Why so loud?

21:31.040 --> 21:32.640
What's going on with you two?

21:32.640 --> 21:34.080
Qingfang, what's wrong?

21:34.840 --> 21:35.200
Okay.

21:38.640 --> 21:39.400
Are you crying,

21:39.400 --> 21:40.840
Xiaocen?

21:43.040 --> 21:44.400
Don't cry.

21:47.720 --> 21:48.850
Don't cry, Xiaocen.

22:00.400 --> 22:01.760
I haven't finished watching.

22:01.760 --> 22:03.490
Why did you change the channel?

22:09.560 --> 22:10.360
Hurry up.

22:11.040 --> 22:11.900
Stop watching.

22:12.480 --> 22:13.210
It's so late.

22:14.200 --> 22:15.760
Put this on the table.

22:17.000 --> 22:18.400
No playing, understand?

22:18.400 --> 22:18.920
Got it.

22:19.040 --> 22:19.900
Go to sleep now.

22:31.080 --> 22:32.340
Just say what you want.

22:32.640 --> 22:34.040
Why are you looking at me?

22:45.200 --> 22:45.800
Qingfang,

22:47.480 --> 22:48.080
are you

22:48.320 --> 22:49.880
really going to change Xiaocen's major?

22:49.880 --> 22:50.400
Yes.

22:51.800 --> 22:54.160
I'm not making this decision out of anger.

22:54.560 --> 22:56.640
Her father and I have already discussed it.

22:56.640 --> 22:59.520
She shouldn't have chosen this major in the first place.

22:59.520 --> 23:01.800
Who knew this major would be so exhausting?

23:01.800 --> 23:03.400
How could her health be good?

23:05.120 --> 23:07.920
Xiaocen's allergy this time was just an accident.

23:08.200 --> 23:08.840
Aren't you

23:09.040 --> 23:11.040
making a mountain out of a molehill?

23:12.120 --> 23:12.720
What if

23:13.280 --> 23:14.880
you change her major,

23:15.080 --> 23:15.480
and she

23:15.640 --> 23:17.200
is still unhappy there?

23:17.520 --> 23:19.040
Then she just won't work.

23:19.120 --> 23:20.280
I'll support her for the rest of her life.

23:20.280 --> 23:20.840
So what?

23:21.080 --> 23:22.880
Can't I support my own daughter?

23:27.120 --> 23:28.040
Don't you think

23:28.680 --> 23:30.560
Xiaocen is very happy every day

23:30.560 --> 23:31.960
in her current major?

23:32.080 --> 23:34.280
She can't risk her life just to be happy.

23:34.680 --> 23:35.920
It's not that serious.

23:35.920 --> 23:37.080
It is that serious.

23:41.120 --> 23:42.720
It's not like you don't know.

23:43.920 --> 23:45.450
I've already made a mistake

23:45.480 --> 23:46.840
with Xiaocen,

23:46.840 --> 23:48.440
and I can't make a second one.

23:52.080 --> 23:52.920
This child

23:53.640 --> 23:55.640
has always been prone to allergies since she was little.

23:55.640 --> 23:56.880
I was very careful.

23:57.000 --> 23:58.000
But that one time,

23:58.400 --> 23:59.840
I worked overtime and came home late.

23:59.840 --> 24:01.700
She ate the shrimp from the fridge

24:01.800 --> 24:03.000
and stayed in that hospital

24:03.000 --> 24:04.400
for a whole month.

24:05.120 --> 24:06.600
How can I not worry?

24:07.720 --> 24:09.680
Isn't that from a long time ago?

24:10.000 --> 24:12.060
Xiaocen is doing fine now, isn't she?

24:15.600 --> 24:16.160
Besides,

24:16.840 --> 24:18.240
making her change majors

24:18.600 --> 24:20.860
isn't just because of her health, right?

24:22.200 --> 24:23.480
I heard from Xing

24:23.520 --> 24:25.320
that a boy often walks her home,

24:25.880 --> 24:26.280
right?

24:27.200 --> 24:29.200
Then tell me, am I wrong to intervene?

24:29.200 --> 24:30.680
Xiaocen is old enough.

24:30.680 --> 24:32.400
It's normal for her to date.

24:32.400 --> 24:34.120
You also dated at Xiaocen's age.

24:34.120 --> 24:35.450
And what was the result?

24:37.640 --> 24:38.560
So,

24:39.120 --> 24:40.320
don't try to persuade me.

24:40.320 --> 24:41.160
I've already decided.
